Version 4.01-unreleased
=======================

* removed memory leak (thanks to wendy)

* implemented Woflan parser

* caged lexer and parser in classes (i.e. cleaned up global namespace)

* added a parameter `--guessFormula' to the frontend tool to guess the
  final condition from the structure of the net (i.e., use the sink place)


See file ChangeLog <http://service-technology.org/files/pnapi/ChangeLog> for
complete version history.

